quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  63,1,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jab yeh munafiq tumahray paas atay hain to kehte hain"" hum gawahi dete hain ke aa p yaqeenan Allah ke rasool hain"" haan, Allah jaanta hai ke tum zaroor uss ke rasool ho, magar Allah gawahi deta hai ke yeh munafiq qatee jhutay hain"
  63,2,unhon ne apni qasmon ko dhaal bana rakha hai aur iss terhan yeh Allah ke rastay se khud ruktay aur duniya ko roktay hain kaisi buri harkatein hain jo yeh log kar rahay hain
  63,3,"yeh sab kuch is wajah se hai ke un logon ne imaan laa kar phir kufar kya is liye un ke dilon par mohar laga di gayi, ab yeh kuch nahi samajte"
  63,4,"iِnhin dekho to inn ke jussay tumhe barray shandaar nazar ayen bolein to tum un ki baatein suntay reh jao magar asal mein yeh goya lakri ke کندے hain jo deewar ke sath chunn kar rakh diye gay hon har zor ki aawaz ko yeh apne khilaaf samajte hain yeh pakkay dushman hain, un se bach kar raho, Allah ki maar un par, yeh kidhar ultay payra-ay ja rahay hain"
  63,5,"aur jab inn se kaha jata hai ke aao taakay Allah ka rasool tumahray liye mughfirat ki dua kere, tu sar jhataktay hain aur tum dekhte ho ke woh barray ghamand ke sath anay se ruktay hain"
  63,6,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum chahay un ke liye mughfirat ki dua karo ya nah karo, un ke liye yaksaa hai, Allah hargiz inhen maaf nah kere ga, Allah fasik logon ko hargiz hadaayat nahi deta"
  63,7,"yeh wohi log hain jo kehte hain ke rasool ke sathiyon par kharch karna band kar do taakay yeh muntashir ho jayen halaank zameen aur asmano ke khazanon ka maalik Allah hi hai, magar yeh munafiq samajte nahi hain"
  63,8,"yeh kehte hain ke hum madeeney wapas poanch jayen to jo izzat wala hai woh zaleel ko wahan se nikaal bahar kere ga halaank izzat to Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam aur momnin ke liye hai, magar yeh munafiq jantay nahi hain"
  63,9,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumahray maal aur tumhari avladin tum ko Allah ki yaad se ghaafil nah kar den jo log aisa karen wohi khasaray mein rehne walay hain"
  63,10,"jo rizaq hum ne tumhe diya hai is mein se kharch karo qabal is ke ke tum mein se kisi ki mout ka waqt aa jaye aur uss waqt woh kahe ke"" ae mere rab, kyun nah to ne mujhe thori si mohlat aur day di ke mein sadqa deta aur Saleh logon mein shaamil ho jata """
  63,11,"halaank jab kisi ki mohlat amal poori honay ka waqt aa jata hai to Allah uss ko hargiz mazeed mohlat nahi deta, aur jo kuch tum karte ho, Allah is se bakhabar hai"
